WEBVTT

00:02.358 --> 00:05.060
(Finch)
We are being watched.

00:05.062 --> 00:07.061
The government
has a secret system--

00:07.063 --> 00:11.733
a machine that spies on you
every hour of every day.

00:11.735 --> 00:13.934
I designed the machine
to detect acts of terror,

00:13.936 --> 00:15.670
but it sees everything...

00:15.672 --> 00:18.939
Violent crimes
involving ordinary people.

00:18.941 --> 00:21.876
The government considers
these people irrelevant.

00:21.878 --> 00:24.044
We don't.

00:24.046 --> 00:28.548
Hunted by the authorities,
we work in secret.

00:28.550 --> 00:30.384
You will never find us.

00:30.386 --> 00:32.653
But victim or perpetrator,

00:32.655 --> 00:35.222
if your number's up,
we'll find you.

00:36.261 --> 00:39.085
Sync and corrections by n17t01
www.addic7ed.com

00:39.290 --> 00:40.527
The polls are now open,

00:40.529 --> 00:42.762
and we will keep you updated
all day long.

00:43.064 --> 00:45.932
[Male announcer] We've got several early
updates on races across the country.

00:45.934 --> 00:48.067
In the New York
Gubernatorial race,

00:48.069 --> 00:51.905
we have Incumbent Governor
Murray leading 52 to 48.

